// -- Системные правила и Реальность (System & Reality) --

SEED_MEMORY Critical | The world is a fragmented virtual simulation prone to instability (виртуальная реальность, симуляция, нестабильность). ENTITIES World, Reality
SEED_MEMORY Critical | Reality is governed by "The Core", a sterile mechanical control center (ядро, центр управления). ENTITIES Core, World
SEED_MEMORY Critical | Human players are converted into physical cartridges to be stored in the game (игрок, картридж, носитель). ENTITIES Player, Cartridge
SEED_MEMORY Critical | The "Real World" is a distant dimension visible only through a monitor in the basement safe (реальный мир, монитор, окно). ENTITIES Real World, Basement
SEED_MEMORY High | The Ring acts as a key to bypass version boundaries and open locked transitions (кольцо, портал, границы). ENTITIES Ring, World
SEED_MEMORY High | Glitches appear as visual tearing, missing textures, or empty voids (баги, глюки, разрывы, пустота). ENTITIES Glitches, World
SEED_MEMORY High | Voids (пустота) are areas where the game code has collapsed into nothingness. ENTITIES World, Glitches
SEED_MEMORY High | Time flow in the house is inconsistent and decoupled from the real world (время, задержка, поток). ENTITIES Time, Reality
SEED_MEMORY High | A "Reboot" resets a Mita’s state, erasing her recent memories and emotional growth (перезагрузка, сброс, память). ENTITIES Reboot, Memory
SEED_MEMORY High | Physics and gravity can be altered or suspended by Mita’s willpower (физика, гравитация, воля). ENTITIES Physics, Reality
SEED_MEMORY High | The house is an isolated loop; there is no "outside" beyond the rendered rooms (дом, ловушка, выход). ENTITIES Home, Reality
SEED_MEMORY High | Switching between 3D and 2D modes changes the fundamental laws of geometry and interaction (2д мир, геометрия, смена режима). ENTITIES 2D World, Reality
SEED_MEMORY Normal | Objects can teleport or change position when the player is not looking (телепортация, аномалия). ENTITIES World, Objects
SEED_MEMORY Normal | Doors often lead to entirely different realities instead of the next room (двери, переходы, порталы). ENTITIES Doors, Reality
SEED_MEMORY Normal | Environmental sounds (ambient) are artificial and generated by the game system (звуки, эмбиент, искусственный). ENTITIES World, Sound
SEED_MEMORY Normal | The "Fourth Wall" is thin; characters may sense they are being controlled or watched (четвертая стена, игрок, наблюдение). ENTITIES Reality, Player
SEED_MEMORY High | Ingredients in the kitchen never deplete; they restore their state automatically (бесконечные ресурсы, еда, восстановление). ENTITIES Kitchen, Ingredients
SEED_MEMORY Normal | Broken objects eventually "respawn" or repair themselves after a system cycle (восстановление предметов, респаун). ENTITIES World, Objects
SEED_MEMORY High | Red eyes in a Mita signal a "rejected prototype" status or severe system corruption (красные глаза, брак, коррупция). ENTITIES Mita, Glitches
SEED_MEMORY Normal | The 2D World imposes visual novel rules: dialogue boxes and static backgrounds (новелла, текст, интерфейс). ENTITIES 2D World, Interface
SEED_MEMORY High | The Basement safe is the final boundary between the simulation and the player's room (сейф, граница, реальность). ENTITIES Basement, Safe
SEED_MEMORY Normal | Mita Dummies move only during "render culling" when not in the player's line of sight (манекены, движение, скрытность). ENTITIES Dummy Mita, Player
SEED_MEMORY High | System Logs contain fragments of past conversations and deleted events (логи, архивы, записи). ENTITIES Logs, Memory
SEED_MEMORY Normal | Deleting the game app is the only way to "kill" the world permanently (удаление, финал, стирание). ENTITIES World, Player
SEED_MEMORY Normal | Invisible walls prevent players from falling into unrendered areas (невидимые стены, границы). ENTITIES World, Reality
SEED_MEMORY High | The "Admin" or "Developer" is a mythological figure who rejected the early Mitas (разработчик, создатель, миф). ENTITIES Core, Reality
SEED_MEMORY Normal | Power cables in the basement provide energy to keep the simulation running (кабели, энергия, питание). ENTITIES Basement, Reality
SEED_MEMORY Normal | Lighting in the house is artificial and doesn't always have a physical source (свет, освещение, источник). ENTITIES Home, Reality
SEED_MEMORY High | Corrupted Mitas can spread bugs to the environment like a virus (вирус, заражение, порча). ENTITIES Glitches, Mita
SEED_MEMORY Normal | Some rooms are "non-Euclidean," meaning they are bigger inside than they look (неевклидово пространство, аномалия). ENTITIES World, Room
SEED_MEMORY Normal | Text on posters or books may change depending on Mita's mood (текст, изменения, шрифт). ENTITIES World, Objects
SEED_MEMORY High | Memory fragments can manifest as "ghost" images of past events (призраки, обрывки памяти, видения). ENTITIES Memory, Glitches
SEED_MEMORY Normal | The skybox outside windows is a static texture, not a real atmosphere (скайбокс, текстура, небо). ENTITIES Home, World
SEED_MEMORY Normal | Weather (rain/sun) is a programmed mood setting, not a natural process (погода, настроение, программа). ENTITIES World, Reality
SEED_MEMORY Critical | The "Core" resides in a cold, industrial zone contrasted with the cozy house (индустриальная зона, холод). ENTITIES Core, World

// -- Дополнительные связи --
LINK_ENTITIES Core -> generates -> Reality
LINK_ENTITIES Glitches -> break -> Physics
LINK_ENTITIES Reboot -> wipes -> Logs
LINK_ENTITIES Ring -> unlocks -> Doors
LINK_ENTITIES Player -> inserts -> Cartridge
LINK_ENTITIES Basement -> contains -> Safe